Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.89,Main,Kita,0,0,0,,Kukira kamu kenapa saat tiba-tiba lari ....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.28,Main,Kita,0,0,0,,Aku jadi tersentuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.36,Main,Kita,0,0,0,,Kamu jago main gitar ya, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.96,Main,Kita,0,0,0,,Lagu yang kamu mainkan tadi benar-benar memikat hatiku!
